Name:		guile
Version:	1.3
Release:	4
Copyright:	GPL
Group:		Development/Languages
Group(pl):	Programowanie/Jêzyki
Source:		ftp://prep.ai.mit.edu/pub/gnu/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
Patch:		guile-libtool.patch
Prereq:		/sbin/install-info
Conflicts:	glibc <= 2.0.7
